[
  {
    "content_id": 797958,
    "reference_id": 19168,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001001-25001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>第一章哀悼耶路撒冷城的毀壞與荒涼，承認這是神對以色列的罪孽所施的應得的審判。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:1",
          "end_ref": "25001022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797966,
    "reference_id": 19176,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>一切所親愛的是指那些掌管生育的神祇——巴力和亞舍拉，多數猶大人都崇拜它們。她的朋友是指她的軍事盟友，尤其是指埃及，但其不是巴比倫的對手（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:5-Jer37:11\">耶37:5–11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:2",
          "end_ref": "25001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797967,
    "reference_id": 19177,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:1\">一章1節</a>中的婦人（和合本譯為：寡婦）是指猶大國。</p></li><li><p>被擄走（和合本譯為：因遭遇苦難……就遷到外邦）：這事發生了四次：公元前605年（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:3-Dan1:4\">但1:3–4</a>）；公元前597年（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:12-2Kgs24:16\">王下24:12–16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:28\">耶52:28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:2-Ezek1:3\">結1:2–3</a>）；公元前586年（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:5-2Kgs25:7\">王下25:5–7</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:18-2Kgs25:21\">18–21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:5-Jer39:10\">耶39:5–10</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:29\">52:29</a>）；以及公元前581年（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:30\">耶52:30</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:3",
          "end_ref": "25001003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797968,
    "reference_id": 19178,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>耶路撒冷（和合本譯為：錫安；希伯來文<em>Zion</em>）：在詩篇和先知書中，錫安代表耶路撒冷城。在耶利米哀歌中，錫安是這座城詩意的名字，即便它如今在一片廢墟中。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22-Heb12:24\">希伯來書十二章22至24節</a>談到了天上的錫安山（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:1-Rev14:5\">啟14:1–5</a>）。</p></li><li><p>耶路撒冷一年一度的節期包括了逾越節、無酵節、初熟節、收割節（五旬節）、吹角節、贖罪日和住棚節。</p></li><li><p>祭司的主要職責是在聖殿並圍繞著聖殿展開的。聖殿已成廢墟，他們因此無事可做，也失去了未來。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:4",
          "end_ref": "25001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797969,
    "reference_id": 19179,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>她許多的罪過：巴比倫入侵之前，猶大的罪行被紀錄在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:1-2Kgs21:9\">列王紀下二十一章1至9節</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:16\">16節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:3-2Kgs24:4\">二十四章3至4節</a>（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:1-2Chr33:10\">代下33:1–10</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:22-2Chr33:23\">22–23</a>和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:11-2Chr36:16\">代下36:11–16</a>）。同樣地，亞述摧毀以色列之前，其罪行紀錄可在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:14-2Kgs17:23\">列王紀下十七章14至23節</a>中被找到。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:5",
          "end_ref": "25001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797970,
    "reference_id": 19180,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>因她跌倒嗤笑（和合本譯為：因她的荒涼嗤笑）：另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:9\">耶利米書二十四章9節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:5\">以西結書二十二章5節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:4\">三十六章4節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:7",
          "end_ref": "25001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797971,
    "reference_id": 19181,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:8–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001008-25001009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶路撒冷失去了人們所珍視的一切物質及屬靈財富。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:8",
          "end_ref": "25001009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797959,
    "reference_id": 19169,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>有關這些事的歷史記載，見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:8-2Kgs25:17\">列王紀下二十五章8至17節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:13-2Chr36:21\">歷代志下三十六章13至21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:4-Jer52:30\">耶利米書五十二章4至30節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:10",
          "end_ref": "25001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797960,
    "reference_id": 19170,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>巴比倫人帶給耶路撒冷的毀滅如同自高天降下的火一般。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:13",
          "end_ref": "25001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797961,
    "reference_id": 19171,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>猶大百姓因為自己的罪而遭軛繩束縛在一起，且作為俘虜被擄。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001014",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:14",
          "end_ref": "25001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797962,
    "reference_id": 19172,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>祂所愛的城（和合本譯為：猶大居民）：神特別眷顧耶路撒冷，就像父親保護祂的女兒一樣。但因她持續不斷的罪行，她因此有可怕的刑罰。</p></li><li><p>像在酒醡中一樣：這種常見的榨葡萄汁的過程在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:3\">以賽亞書六十三章3節</a>中是用來生動地顯示刑罰之恐怖。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:18-Rev14:20\">啟示錄十四章18至20節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:15\">十九章15節</a>中，這個意象生動地代表了對全世界的審判。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:15",
          "end_ref": "25001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797963,
    "reference_id": 19173,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>我懇求我的盟友（和合本譯為：我招呼我所親愛的）：埃及很在意猶大，因為猶大控制著通往北方的唯一一條好路。然而，當巴比倫攻擊耶路撒冷時，埃及卻背棄了猶大（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:5-Jer37:11\">耶37:5–11</a>）。</p></li><li><p>當巴勒斯坦的秋季和春季雨水稀少時，無雨的夏季就可能會毀壞農作物並導致糧食短缺。在城遭長期圍困的情況下，糧食供應也會消耗殆盡（公元前588年1月–586年7月），許多人因飢荒而死（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:2-2Kgs25:3\">王下25:2–3</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">耶37:21</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:19",
          "end_ref": "25001019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797964,
    "reference_id": 19174,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>猶大的領袖和百姓悖逆（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:17\">耶2:17</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:6\">5:6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:23\">23</a>），因他們拒絕了唯一的真神以及祂的誡命，並且背叛了神所派遣的入侵者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:1\">王下24:1</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:20\">20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:13\">代下36:13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:20",
          "end_ref": "25001020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797965,
    "reference_id": 19175,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 1:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你所應許的那日（和合本譯為：你報告的日子）：詩人相信神會設立一個日子，到那日，所有人——壓迫者和受迫害者——都能得到公正的審判，他因此感到振奮（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:6\">賽13:6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:9\">9</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:10-Jer46:12\">耶46:10–12</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer46:27-Jer46:28\">27–28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:18-Amos5:20\">摩5:18–20</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:15\">俄1:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:2-1Thess5:3\">前帖前5:2–3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:2\">帖後2:2</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25001021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:21",
          "end_ref": "25001021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 1:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797978,
    "reference_id": 19188,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>從天：耶路撒冷的建築華麗壯觀，裝飾著貴重的金屬和寶石。耶路撒冷作為耶和華的聖城而享有聲譽。</p></li><li><p>祂的聖殿（和合本譯為：自己的腳凳；字面意思是<em>他的腳凳</em>）：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:2\">歷代志上二十八章2節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:5\">詩篇九十九篇5節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps132:7\">一三二篇7節</a>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:1",
          "end_ref": "25002001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797972,
    "reference_id": 19182,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002001-25002022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>本章生動地描繪了耶和華是耶路撒冷的毀滅者。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:1",
          "end_ref": "25002022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797981,
    "reference_id": 19191,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:3–4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002003-25002004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>張弓：過去，耶和華曾是以色列大能的戰士（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:13-Exod15:21\">出14:13–15:21</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:9-Josh23:11\">書23:9–11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:1-Judg7:25\">士7章</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:32-2Kgs19:35\">王下19:32–35</a>）；現在祂向耶路撒冷發動戰爭（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10\">賽63:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:25\">結24:25</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:3",
          "end_ref": "25002004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797982,
    "reference_id": 19192,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>園中的窩棚是一個臨時的搭建物，收割者搭建它以供遮蔭。神曾應許要永遠照看祂的聖殿（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:3\">王上9:3</a>），但現在似乎祂已經離棄了它。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:6",
          "end_ref": "25002006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797983,
    "reference_id": 19193,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>聖殿被毀是因祭司和百姓在其牆垣內所犯之罪，玷污了其聖潔（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:3-Jer7:15\">耶7:3–15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:3-Jer26:6\">26:3–6</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:12-Jer26:13\">12–13</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:21\">結24:21</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:7",
          "end_ref": "25002007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797984,
    "reference_id": 19194,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>外郭是堆砌在城四圍的石牆或土堆，好在敵軍進攻時用於護衛城。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:8",
          "end_ref": "25002008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797985,
    "reference_id": 19195,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>不得見……異象：但以理和以西結是耶和華的先知，他們生活在遠離猶大地的被擄者中時曾得見異象（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:1\">結1:1</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:1\">但7:1</a>）。這節經文是指在耶路撒冷的先知，他們聲稱見到了異象，但卻被證明是假的異象。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:9",
          "end_ref": "25002009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797973,
    "reference_id": 19183,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>麻布（或<em>粗麻布</em>）是用山羊或駱駝毛製成的袋子，通常用於裝穀物或裝牲畜馱運的貨物。因為它便宜，所以窮人用它來作衣服，而哀悼的人穿著它作為表達深切悲傷的標誌（它暗沉的顏色與他們的情緒相符，它的粗糙與他們的難受相符）。</p></li><li><p>在頭上和衣服上揚起塵土是向鄰居表示家人去世的標誌。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:10",
          "end_ref": "25002010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797974,
    "reference_id": 19184,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>誰能醫治你呢？有名望的醫治者和先知都是騙子和<span>虛假的說謊</span>者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13-Jer6:14\">耶6:13–14</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002013",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:13",
          "end_ref": "25002013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797975,
    "reference_id": 19185,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>他們的仇敵對耶路撒冷所遭遇的落敗感到高興。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:16",
          "end_ref": "25002016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:16"
        }
