    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797976,
    "reference_id": 19186,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>他所定的……他古時所命定的：神的祝福應許永遠取決於以色列是否遵行律法（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:1-Deut8:20\">申8章</a>）。如果他們不遵行，祂曾命定要毀滅他們（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1-Lev26:46\">利26章</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002017",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:17",
          "end_ref": "25002017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797977,
    "reference_id": 19187,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:18–19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002018-25002019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>面對神的審判之毀滅，悔改和禱告才是正確的回應。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:18",
          "end_ref": "25002019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797979,
    "reference_id": 19189,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶利米曾預言，在撒馬利亞圍城期間所發生的<span>自相殘殺的</span>事件（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:28-2Kgs6:29\">王下6:28–29</a>），將會發生在耶路撒冷（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:9\">耶19:9</a>；另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:10\">哀4:10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:10\">結5:10</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:53-Deut28:57\">申28:53–57</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:20",
          "end_ref": "25002020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797980,
    "reference_id": 19190,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 2:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>像在大會的日子招聚人一樣：詩人將耶路撒冷的毀滅比喻為邀請人參加一場宴會，在這場宴會上，戰爭、饑荒、野生動物和疾病將在耶路撒冷吞噬惡人（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:68\">申28:15–68</a>；參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:17-Rev19:21\">啟19:17–21</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25002022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:22",
          "end_ref": "25002022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 2:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797986,
    "reference_id": 19196,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:1–24",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003001-25003024",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>作者說猶大和耶路撒冷的苦難就是他自身的苦難。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:1",
          "end_ref": "25003024",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:24"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797987,
    "reference_id": 19197,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:1–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003001-25003066",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在本章中，作者為所發生的事哀悼（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:1-Lam3:20\">3:1–20</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:48-Lam3:54\">48–54</a>）、紀念耶和華的信實與慈愛（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:21-Lam3:25\">3:21–25</a>）、描述神的子民該如何回應（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:26-Lam3:47\">3:26–47</a>），並在禱告中呼求耶和華（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:55-Lam3:66\">3:55–66</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:1",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798004,
    "reference_id": 19214,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:6–9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003006-25003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>有些人將這段經文理解為對耶路撒冷被毀前，耶利米困於淤泥牢獄中之經歷的詩意描述（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6-Jer38:13\">耶38:6–13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:6",
          "end_ref": "25003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798006,
    "reference_id": 19216,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>擋住我的道……使我的路彎曲：罪會造成混亂，並使一個人或群體與幸福的未來隔絕。清潔的人看到的未來是一條易於遵循的直路（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:8\">箴21:8</a>）。以賽亞將神的活動想像為一個在直路上前行的隊伍，而祂的敬拜者們會為祂遇備這條道路（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:3\">賽40:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:9",
          "end_ref": "25003009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797988,
    "reference_id": 19198,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:4\">約伯記六章4節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:12",
          "end_ref": "25003012",
