    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797989,
    "reference_id": 19199,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>苦不堪言（或<em>如同茵蔯和苦膽</em>；和合本譯為：如茵蔯和苦膽的困苦窘迫）：茵蔯是一種味道苦澀的植物，在這裡反應了內心的痛苦情感之烈（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:4\">箴5:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:11\">啟8:11</a>）。苦膽是一種有毒植物，若食用會引起身體劇烈的疼痛，它強烈地象徵了極度重壓下的情緒（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:18\">申29:18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:21\">詩69:21</a>）。作者似乎陷入了一個無法逃脫的絕境。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:19",
          "end_ref": "25003019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797991,
    "reference_id": 19201,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華信實的慈愛是詩人從深度憂鬱中得以恢復的基礎。就像耶利米在牢獄中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6-Jer38:13\">耶38:6–13</a>）以及約拿在大魚腹中（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:2-Jonah2:10\">拿2:2–10</a>）時所經歷的一樣，耶和華從死亡中賜下拯救。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:22",
          "end_ref": "25003022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797990,
    "reference_id": 19200,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:22–33",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003022-25003033",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神的慈愛和信實永不斷絕。正如神因耶路撒冷的罪而降下審判是信實的一樣，祂也會信實地醫治那些轉向祂的人。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:22",
          "end_ref": "25003033",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:33"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797992,
    "reference_id": 19202,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神的信實顯示出祂絕對可靠，而這顯明在祂每日的憐憫中。祂持續地供應給我們一個適合居住的世界，使我們得以存活。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:23",
          "end_ref": "25003023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797993,
    "reference_id": 19203,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:24",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003024",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶和華是我的分：自摩西時代以來，迦南地一直被視為以色列的產業（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:17\">出15:17</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:19\">書21:19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:8\">代上28:8</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:4\">詩47:4</a>），但神子民真正的產業是神本身（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:5-Ps16:6\">詩16:5–6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">弗1:11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">來9:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:4\">彼前1:3–4</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003024",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:24",
          "end_ref": "25003024",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:24"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797994,
    "reference_id": 19204,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:26",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003026",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>那些對神的計劃有信心的人，能夠靜默等候祂的救恩。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003026",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:26",
          "end_ref": "25003026",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:26"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797995,
    "reference_id": 19205,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:28",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003028",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>獨坐無言：謙卑地順服，止住舌頭，使心靈安靜。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003028",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:28",
          "end_ref": "25003028",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:28"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797996,
    "reference_id": 19206,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:29–30",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003029-25003030",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>在古代近東，<span>口貼塵埃</span>表示服從（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:1-Gen17:3\">創17:1–3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:24\">利9:24</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:6\">書7:6</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:4\">撒上5:4</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:39\">王上18:39</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:16\">代上21:16</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5-Matt17:6\">太17:5–6</a>）。</p></li><li><p>轉過另一邊臉頰（和合本譯為：由人打他的腮頰）也表示服從。當耶穌在教導門徒當忍受逼迫時（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:39\">太5:39</a>），祂顯然想到了這節經文。這樣的回應承認了，<span>神甚至在我們的苦難中也是掌權者</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003029",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:29",
          "end_ref": "25003030",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:30"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797997,
    "reference_id": 19207,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:31",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003031",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:8-Ps103:11\">詩篇一〇三篇8至11節</a>。</p>",
