  {
    "content_id": 797998,
    "reference_id": 19208,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:34–36",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003034-25003036",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>猶大人在耶路撒冷被毀前就行了這些事（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26-Jer5:31\">耶5:26–31</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:11-Jer21:14\">21:11–14</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:10-Jer23:14\">23:10–14</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:1-Mic3:12\">彌3章</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003034",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:34",
          "end_ref": "25003036",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:36"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 797999,
    "reference_id": 19209,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:37–39",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003037-25003039",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>有些災難是自然原因造成的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:1-Luke13:5\">路13:1–5</a>），且壞事會同樣地發生在義人和惡人身上（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">太5:45</a>）；但無論發生什麼事，我們都應該獻上感謝（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">帖前5:18</a>）而非抱怨。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003037",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:37",
          "end_ref": "25003039",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:39"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798000,
    "reference_id": 19210,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:40–42",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003040-25003042",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>悔改是領受救恩的關鍵（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:27\">賽1:27</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:22\">耶3:22</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:21\">結3:21</a>）。</p>",
