  },
  {
    "content_id": 798001,
    "reference_id": 19211,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:48–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003048-25003066",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>作者聚焦於仇敵的惡毒，向耶和華呼求幫助。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003048",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:48",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798002,
    "reference_id": 19212,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:52–57",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003052-25003057",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這段經文可能是指耶利米在獄中的經歷（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:11-Jer37:15\">耶37:11–15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:1-Jer38:13\">38:1–13</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003052",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:52",
          "end_ref": "25003057",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:57"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798003,
    "reference_id": 19213,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:58–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003058-25003066",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>耶路撒冷應受懲罰，但敵人卻以不該有的殘酷手段施行刑罰。作者呼籲神懲治他們。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003058",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:58",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798005,
    "reference_id": 19215,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 3:64–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003064-25003066",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這個報復的禱告與詩篇中的幾篇類似（見「<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203217\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesThemes\">報復的禱告</span>」主題註釋）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003064",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:64",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 203217,
          "content_id": 700280,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotesThemes",
          "label": "為報復的禱告",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798007,
    "reference_id": 19217,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004001-25004022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>雖然神的子民仍在經歷祂的審判，但他們很快就會迎來復興。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:1",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798014,
    "reference_id": 19224,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004003",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>好像……鴕鳥一般：另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:13-Job39:16\">約伯記三十九章13至16節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:3",
          "end_ref": "25004003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798015,
    "reference_id": 19225,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>像光潤的藍寶石一樣（字面意思是<em>如同青金石）</em>：青金石是一種美麗的藍色石頭，質地柔軟、適合雕刻，常用於裝飾和鑲嵌藝術。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:7",
          "end_ref": "25004007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798016,
    "reference_id": 19226,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004008",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>皮膚緊貼骨頭是餓死之前的症狀。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:8",
          "end_ref": "25004008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798017,
    "reference_id": 19227,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004009",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>長期遭圍困導致嚴重的食物短缺。即便人們能到田地裡，他們也會發現作物已遭摧毀，或已被收割用於餵養士兵。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:9",
          "end_ref": "25004009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798008,
    "reference_id": 19218,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004012",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>地上的君王……能進耶路撒冷的城門：因為神在一個多世紀前，從亞述的西拿基立手中拯救了耶路撒冷（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:36-2Kgs19:37\">王下19:36–37</a>），因此猶大人堅信即便是巴比倫的尼布甲尼撒這位最強大的君王，也無法擊敗這座城。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:12",
          "end_ref": "25004012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798009,
    "reference_id": 19219,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這些領袖看起來是以難民的身分從耶路撒冷逃往其它地方。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:15",
          "end_ref": "25004015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798010,
    "reference_id": 19220,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我們的王（和合本譯為：耶和華的受膏者）……被捉住：這指的是西底家，他試圖逃跑但被捉住，且尼布甲尼撒殘忍地對待他（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:4-2Kgs25:7\">王下25:4–7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:4-Jer39:7\">耶39:4–7</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:9-Jer52:11\">52:9–11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:20",
          "end_ref": "25004020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798012,
    "reference_id": 19222,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>烏斯是約旦河東的一個地區，向南延伸到以東。這裡是約伯的家鄉（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1\">伯1:1</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21",
          "end_ref": "25004021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798011,
    "reference_id": 19221,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:21–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004021-25004022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以東人覺得安全了，並為耶路撒冷所遭遇的不幸而幸災樂禍，但他們也將因自己的罪受刑罰（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:1-Obad1:21\">俄1章</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:7-Jer49:22\">耶49:7–22</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798013,
    "reference_id": 19223,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 4:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>被擄後第一次歸回是在公元前538年，當時波斯的塞魯士擊敗了巴比倫（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22-2Chr36:23\">代下36:22–23</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:4\">拉1:1–4</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798018,
    "reference_id": 19228,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 5:1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005001-25005022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這一章是一個誠摯的祈求復興的禱告（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:19\">但9:4–19</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:1",
          "end_ref": "25005022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798019,
    "reference_id": 19229,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 5:10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>在圍困期間，城內發生了飢荒（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:3\">王下25:3</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">耶37:21</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:9\">38:9</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:6\">52:6</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:10",
          "end_ref": "25005010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798020,
    "reference_id": 19230,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 5:12–17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005012-25005017",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這些可怕的事之所以發生是因為百姓所犯的罪（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:7-Isa24:12\">賽24:7–12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:24\">耶7:24</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:18\">13:18</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:10-Jer25:11\">25:10–11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:10\">摩8:10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:12",
          "end_ref": "25005017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798021,
    "reference_id": 19231,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 5:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>豺狼四處遊蕩（和合本譯為：野狗行在其上）：參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">以賽亞書十三章22節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:13\">三十四章13節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:11\">耶利米書九章11節</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:22\">十章22節</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:3\">瑪拉基書一章3節</a>。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:18",
          "end_ref": "25005018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 798022,
    "reference_id": 19232,
    "title": "耶利米哀歌 5:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>你竟全然棄絕我們……？被擄的悲劇引發了神是否會赦罪並醫治祂的百姓的問題。神透過先知（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:27-Isa40:31\">賽40:27–31</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:8-Isa41:20\">41:8–20</a>）和差遣基督（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:2-Matt9:6\">太9:2–6</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:28\">26:28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:47\">路24:47</a>）明確地回答了這個問題。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:22",
          "end_ref": "25005022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  }
]